    "Name": "Scorpion (RAC)",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Scorpion Light Tank (RAC)</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Inner Sphere</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>4/6 (Tracked)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>100 ICE</color></b>\n\nThe Scorpion tank, produced by Quikscell Company in 2807, is known for its low cost, easy repair, and availability in numbers. Known as \"The Budget Tank\", it is found on many backwater and Periphery worlds.\n\nDeveloped by the Federated Suns in the 3060s, this variant upgrades the main gun to a Rotary AC/2 for which it carries a single ton of ammunition. It retains an internal combustion engine but does make use of ferro-fibrous armor technology.",
